    <title>Python3 网络编程（使用Socket实现TCP、UDP通信）</title>
    <link href="https://xin02.github.io/2021/06/04/Python3%20%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Socket%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0TCP%E3%80%81UDP%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>https://xin02.github.io/2021/06/04/Python3%20%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Socket%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0TCP%E3%80%81UDP%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%89/</id>
